  <span id="freeText17463487904532346590" style="display:none">This review should have a spoiler format. I’m glad knowing a key development didn’t ruin the relationship/book for you, but that doesn’t mean you should decide for others. This review states outright something that in the book evolves and reveals itself slowly, so that you can experience it the way Evelyn did, unless you accidentally read this review first. Glad I didn’t.</span>
