      <a class="smallText greyText" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link244852823" title="Flag this comment as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=244852823&amp;resource_type=Comment&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F33161050-the-seven-husbands-of-evelyn-hugo">flag</a>    

