<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12077622585749491202">Taylor Jenkins Reid is the New York Times bestselling author of Malibu Rising, Daisy Jones &amp; The Six, and The Seven Husbands of Evelyn Hugo, as well as four other novels. Her newest novel, Malibu Rising, is out now. She lives in Los Angeles. You can follow her on Instagram <a href='https://www.instagram.com/tjenkinsreid/' rel='nofollow noopener'>@tjenkinsreid</a>.</span>
  <span id="freeText12077622585749491202" style="display:none">Taylor Jenkins Reid is the New York Times bestselling author of Malibu Rising, Daisy Jones &amp; The Six, and The Seven Husbands of Evelyn Hugo, as well as four other novels. Her newest novel, Malibu Rising, is out now. She lives in Los Angeles. You can follow her on Instagram <a href="https://www.instagram.com/tjenkinsreid/" rel="nofollow noopener">@tjenkinsreid</a>.</span>
